<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">周照根：</span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">男，毕业于浙江师范大学，本科学历，应用电子技术教育专业。中学一级教师，维修电工技师。现主要任教</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><font face="Times New Roman">PLC</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">工业学科。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">周老师现任电子电工组组长，教学能力突出。任职以来获得</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">2008</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">年嘉兴市中职学校青年教师业务能力竞赛维修电工项目二等奖；<span lang="EN-US">2009</span>年嘉兴市中职学校专业教师业务能力竞赛获命题项目竞赛三等奖；<span lang="EN-US">2009</span>年校青年教师同课异构教学设计比赛荣获校二等奖</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">；<span lang="EN-US">2010</span>年嘉兴市中职学校教师专业技能比赛，获得了电子产品装接与调试二等奖以及<span lang="EN-US">2010</span>年度获校&ldquo;敬精明星&rdquo;。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">技能竞赛方面，所带学生在无线电装接与调试（<span lang="EN-US">A</span>组）项目上获嘉兴市一等奖<span lang="EN-US">3</span>人、二等奖<span lang="EN-US">1</span>人、三等奖<span lang="EN-US">1</span>人。浙江省一等奖<span lang="EN-US">1</span>人、三等奖<span lang="EN-US">1</span>人。并在全国比赛中获三等奖。自己多次被评为嘉兴市优秀<span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">辅导教师称号。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体">周老师所写的论文获嘉兴市中职学校论文评比二等奖<span lang="EN-US">2</span>篇、三等奖<span lang="EN-US">2</span>篇；获平湖市优秀教育教学论文三等奖<span lang="EN-US">1</span>篇。负责编写的校本教材《电子产品装配技术基础》已在校高一年级中试用；参与编写的教材《电子电工基础实训》入选<span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">普通高中选修课程资源库。</span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '', '', '30', '2', '0', '', '', '无', '', '0', '0', '0')
