family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年被评为平湖市教育系统优秀党员。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">盛老师的论文获浙江省职教论文三等奖</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><font face="Times New Roman">3</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">篇；浙江省职教论文二等奖</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><font face="Times New Roman">1</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">篇；嘉兴市中职教育教学论文二等奖</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><font face="Times New Roman">1</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">篇。参与编写的教材《电子电工基础实训》入选<span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">普通高中选修课程资源库；</span>负责编写了校本教材《中级维修电工考级实训指导书》。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
