<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang="EN-US">&ldquo;</span>挫折是块磨石，把强者磨得更加坚强，把弱者磨得更加脆弱。<span lang="EN-US">&rdquo;</span>我将通过努力，成为那个强者。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
