<p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 20.58pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: left"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">本书的追求：</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''">教师易教，学生易学，快乐教与学。</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: ''宋体''; mso-spacerun: ''yes''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
