            <td valign="top" width="528" style="border-top: #f0f0f0; height: 170.95pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-right: 5.4pt; width: 396pt; background-color: transparent">
            <div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 6pt; line-height: 125%; text-indent: -6pt"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">一、组织教学</span></b></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">1</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">．课堂相关材料准备。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%"><b><font size="6"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; line-height: 125%">2</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; line-height: 125%">．师生问候，稳定师生情绪。</span></font></b></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">二、课前两分钟演讲</span></b></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 21.6pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">主题为&ldquo;发现美的眼睛&rdquo;</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">三、复习导入</span></b></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black; line-height: 125%">四方连续图案是生活中最常见的装饰纹样之一，由于它具有整齐、规范的特点，所以常常被运用到生活的各个领域作为装饰。</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">我们上节课已经学习了四方连续的概念和基本的构成样式，那么如何根据单元形的特点，选择合适的构成样式进行四方连续纹样的设计是本节课的重点。首先让我们来复习回顾一下上节课的内容</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; line-height: 125%">四方连续的概念：由一个纹样或几个纹样组成一个单位，向四周重复地连续和延伸扩展而成的图案</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 21.6pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">搜索：</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black; line-height: 125%">在教室中找出运用四方连续的物品</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 11.75pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black; line-height: 125%">（墙上装裱书法作品的纸、窗帘、地砖&hellip;&hellip;）</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 11.75pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">再来回忆一下：四方连续的构成样式有哪些？</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">根据单元形的排列顺序，我们可以把构成样式分为三类。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">散点式（平接、斜阶排列）</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">连缀式（菱形连缀、阶梯连缀、波形连缀、转换方向的连缀）</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">重叠式</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">我们已经熟悉了构成样式的基本分类，那么我们现在来看一下黑板上的图片，大家一起来回答：图片中的连续纹样分别运用了什么构成样式？</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt">&nbsp;
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
            <br clear="all" />
            <div style="line-height: 125%"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">四、</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">[</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">游戏</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">]</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">空挡接龙</span></b></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">给出一组四方连续，挖掉其中的一小部分，请同学们找出其中的排列规律，并画出缺失的纹样。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">五、新课讲解</span></b></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 11.75pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">（一）接下来请同学们比较一下黑板上的两幅作品，大家觉得哪一幅更能达到完美的构成效果？</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 17.65pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">展示单元形相同，运用不同构成样式的两幅图案，两相对照，找出弊病，引出本节课讨论的中心问题：如何根据单元形的特点，选用合适的排列方式，使其达到完美的构成效果。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">（二）选用合适的排列方式时遵循的原则</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt">
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">因为四方连续是由</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black; letter-spacing: 0.4pt; line-height: 125%">一个单位形，向四周重复地连续和延伸扩展而成的图案。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24.6pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">我们可以先对它的单位纹样进行分析，然后根据单位纹样的特点，不断地进行尝试，选择合适的构成样式。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 23.95pt"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">1</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">．观察图片</span>a</b><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">与图片</span>a</b><b>＇。</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">两张图片运用了相同的单元形：包括主体物&mdash;&mdash;变形的枫叶，和对角线分割的两个三角形色块两部分。图片</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">a</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">中将单元形进行平接，方向上也没有进行变化，每个单元形之间看起来是独立存在的，联系较少。而当我们将单元形旋转后，每四个三角形成为一组，成为规则的正方形，构成形式也变为了重叠式，枫叶为浮纹，方形为底纹，单元形之间的联系加强。</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">(</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">图片</span>a＇<span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">)</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">在我们的创作过程中也尽可能地多寻找并利用单元形之间的联系。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">这组图片可以归纳出一条原则</span><b><span style="font-size: 14pt; line-height: 125%">&ldquo;骨肉相连&rdquo;</span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">（<b>原则一</b>）</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 12.5pt"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">2</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">．观察第二个单元形：</span></b>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><br clear="all" />
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">分析图片</span><span><span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">b</span></span></span><span><span><span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">：这个四方连续的单位形是由两个纹样组合而成。两个纹样的高度基本相同，但宽度相差较大。如果进行平接，则形与形之间不贴合。</span></span></span></span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span><span><span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">因此我们选择斜排法，单位形之间进行错位排列</span></span></span></span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt">
            <div style="line-height: 125%">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">这组图片可以归纳出一条原则</span> <b><span style="font-size: 14pt; line-height: 125%">&ldquo;见缝插针&rdquo;（</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">原则二）</span></b></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><br clear="all" />
            <div style="line-height: 125%"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">图片</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">c</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">利用六边形规则排列后创作出</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">c</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">＇，单元形之间结合紧密，连贯性较强。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 12.55pt"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">3</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">．再来观察第三个单元形：</span></b>&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 42pt">
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">（图片</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">d</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">）这个四方连续的单位形呈曲线形，本身具有高低落差。利用&ldquo;见缝插针&rdquo;原则，可以画出图片</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">d</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">＇。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">另一种思路：当单元形进行上下或者左右翻转后，也刚好能与原来的单元形贴合。（图片</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">d</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">＇＇，图片</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">d</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">＇＇＇）</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt">
            <div style="line-height: 125%">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">这种思路我们可以归纳出一条原则&ldquo;</span><b><span style="font-size: 14pt; line-height: 125%">逆顺穿插</span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">&rdquo;。</span><b><span style="font-size: 14pt; line-height: 125%">（</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">原则三）</span></b></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 12.55pt"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">4</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">．观察第四个四方连续图案：</span></b></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 11.8pt">&nbsp; <span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">　讨论：图片</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">e</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">存在什么问题？如何改进？</span>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">分析图片</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">e</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">：此四方连续运用了重叠式的构图，底纹采用简单的几何形，浮纹采用玫瑰花形以散点排列。应以浮纹为主，底纹作为衬托。因为底纹的几何线条颜色过深，使得主次不明确。图片</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">e</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">＇将底纹颜色变淡，突出主花，使得主次更加分明</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 24pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">采用这种构成样式时要避免花纹重叠时因为层次不清而陷于杂乱。</span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 11.95pt; line-height: 125%; text-indent: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">这组图片可以归纳出一条原则</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">&ldquo;</span><b><span style="font-size: 14pt; line-height: 125%">虚实有道</span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">&rdquo;</span><b><span style="font-size: 14pt; line-height: 125%">（</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">原则四）。</span></b></div>
            <div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 11.95pt; line-height: 125%; text-indent: 30pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">主要针对重叠式的构图而言</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%"><span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 让学生小结：选用四方连续纹样时应遵循的原则&ldquo;骨肉相连、见缝插针、逆顺穿插、虚实有道&rdquo;</span></span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%"><span>&nbsp;</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">六、练习</span></b></div>
