            <div style="line-height: 125%">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">七、</span></b><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">学生介绍作品，教师适当评讲。</span></b></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%"><b>&nbsp;</b></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%"><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">八、课堂小结</span></b></div>
            <div style="line-height: 125%; text-indent: 18pt"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black; line-height: 125%">四方连续图案是生活中常见的装饰纹样，<span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black; line-height: 125%">我们</span>同学在设计四方连续纹样时应考虑到单元形与</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">构成样式</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black; line-height: 125%">的搭配，做到</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 125%">&ldquo;骨肉相连、见缝插针、逆顺穿插、虚实有道&rdquo;。</span></div>
